cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
This is a pretty good 2009 Nissan Versa with only 75000 miles on it. White and power everything.
This is an okay 2004 Toyota Corolla with only 85000 miles on it. White and power everything.
This is a brand new Subaru Outback with only 100 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything and you only wish you had it.
